pageContext.claim: “We had two congressmen, one who was possibly going to win, he was up by two, he won by about 27, I think, or something like that.”
pageContext.analysis: It’s not clear to which poll Trump is referring. Rep. Greg Murphy (R-N.C.) won handily is a heavily Republican district that Trump won handily in 2016. There’s no indication the seat was ever in jeopardy.
